8
00:00:39,509 --> 00:00:41,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">来 把球打回来</font>

9
00:00:44,399 --> 00:00:46,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">两个人玩沙滩排球有意思吗？</font>

10
00:00:47,519 --> 00:00:50,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">和我一起玩 你不开心吗？</font>

11
00:00:51,519 --> 00:00:53,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不 我也没这个意思…</font>

12
00:00:55,759 --> 00:00:57,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那就去坐那个吧！</font>

13
00:01:01,729 --> 00:01:04,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你真的一秒都不想划啊？</font>

14
00:01:05,579 --> 00:01:09,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这可是你这个仆人值得纪念的第一次工作啊</font>

15
00:01:09,679 --> 00:01:15,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">老实说 就算没这个惩罚 我也感觉一直都被你指使啊</font>

16
00:01:19,529 --> 00:01:21,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没想到你也挺有肌肉的嘛</font>

17
00:01:22,709 --> 00:01:23,829
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">住手啊</font>

18
00:01:25,919 --> 00:01:27,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">反正也没人在看</font>

19
00:01:29,469 --> 00:01:32,679
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没人看就能为所欲为了吗 你这标准真奇怪</font>

20
00:01:36,819 --> 00:01:39,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你真的不开心吗？</font>

21
00:01:40,589 --> 00:01:42,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">倒也不是</font>

22
00:01:44,999 --> 00:01:47,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只是突然发现 我们已经走这么远了</font>

23
00:01:48,709 --> 00:01:54,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">距离在天上和你相遇的那天 已经过去两年了</font>

24
00:01:55,129 --> 00:01:56,519
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在则是在海上</font>

25
00:01:58,039 --> 00:01:58,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">然后呢？</font>

26
00:01:59,629 --> 00:02:02,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你现在开心吗？还是不开心？</font>

27
00:02:04,159 --> 00:02:07,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">等将来这趟旅程结束的时候我就说</font>

28
00:02:09,509 --> 00:02:12,329
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">可以 你就保持现在的你吧</font>

29
00:02:13,429 --> 00:02:17,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过 要想对我表白的话请趁早哦</font>

30
00:02:17,839 --> 00:02:19,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">毕竟我可是很抢手的</font>

31
00:02:19,909 --> 00:02:22,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谁要对你表白啊 而且请不要自夸</font>

32
00:02:23,279 --> 00:02:24,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个先不说了</font>

33
00:02:25,179 --> 00:02:26,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那要说什么？</font>

34
00:02:26,619 --> 00:02:30,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">等我们找到宝藏 吃香喝辣够了之后</font>

35
00:02:30,619 --> 00:02:33,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就找个地方开侦探事务所吧</font>

36
00:02:33,769 --> 00:02:37,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没想到身无分文的人会说出这种话</font>

37
00:02:39,819 --> 00:02:42,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就这样 短暂的暑假过去了</font>

38
00:02:43,559 --> 00:02:48,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">侦探和助手那不讲道理的日子又再次开始了</font>

39
00:02:50,269 --> 00:02:54,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">自从邂逅你的那一天开始</font>

40
00:02:54,269 --> 00:02:59,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我的一切仿佛都被改变</font>

41
00:02:59,609 --> 00:03:01,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(侦探已死)
我的一切仿佛都被改变</font>

42
00:03:01,839 --> 00:03:09,289
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(侦探已死)</font>

43
00:03:10,409 --> 00:03:14,309
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">仿佛做了一个梦</font>

44
00:03:14,609 --> 00:03:20,179
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在已经无法听到的脚步声传来</font>

45
00:03:20,569 --> 00:03:24,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让我张开眼睛</font>

46
00:03:24,639 --> 00:03:27,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却依然孤孤单单</font>

47
00:03:27,219 --> 00:03:29,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我期待的只有那一个人</font>

48
00:03:29,969 --> 00:03:34,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">当初没能对你说的话</font>

49
00:03:34,149 --> 00:03:38,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">依然封存在我心中</font>

50
00:03:40,029 --> 00:03:42,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我在那个世界里</font>

51
00:03:42,339 --> 00:03:44,759
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">找到了重要的东西</font>

52
00:03:44,759 --> 00:03:49,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我一直在渴求着这颗心</font>

53
00:03:49,609 --> 00:03:52,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我和你约定</font>

54
00:03:52,479 --> 00:03:55,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我们要在这里</font>

55
00:03:55,279 --> 00:03:59,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">永远一起欢笑</font>

56
00:04:00,349 --> 00:04:02,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">时光荏苒 直到现在</font>

57
00:04:19,979 --> 00:04:23,989
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(第5集 那是为了一年后的未来)</font>

58
00:04:24,199 --> 00:04:24,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是…</font>

59
00:04:25,589 --> 00:04:27,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">刻耳柏洛斯干的好事吧</font>

60
00:04:27,849 --> 00:04:29,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">刻耳柏洛斯？</font>

61
00:04:30,339 --> 00:04:31,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">声音真奇怪</font>

62
00:04:31,929 --> 00:04:34,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我讨厌血的气味</font>

63
00:04:37,539 --> 00:04:41,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">要么歪脑袋 要么拧鼻子 不要两个都选</font>

64
00:04:42,739 --> 00:04:45,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说的这个刻耳柏洛斯</font>

65
00:04:45,039 --> 00:04:48,389
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">指的就是最近出现的那个开膛手杰克？</font>

66
00:04:49,019 --> 00:04:51,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对 代号「刻耳柏洛斯」</font>

67
00:04:51,999 --> 00:04:56,929
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">代表的是会啃食人类心脏的地狱看门犬</font>

68
00:05:02,169 --> 00:05:03,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">真慢</font>

69
00:05:04,889 --> 00:05:06,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这里禁烟哦</font>

70
00:05:07,339 --> 00:05:08,459
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那就拿去</font>

71
00:05:10,849 --> 00:05:14,239
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">飞机要起飞了 我要回日本去</font>

72
00:05:14,339 --> 00:05:19,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这就走了？话说 风靡小姐你跑来这种地方干什么？</font>

73
00:05:20,429 --> 00:05:24,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">工作调动 不过也只到昨天为止了</font>

74
00:05:24,449 --> 00:05:26,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">从没听说过还有这种人事变动的</font>

75
00:05:27,539 --> 00:05:30,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以这个案子就交给你们了</font>

76
00:05:31,319 --> 00:05:34,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">把这个复活于现代的开膛手杰克逮捕归案</font>

77
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:37,229
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不是 这什么道理啊？</font>

78
00:05:41,669 --> 00:05:44,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不讲道理啊 为什么我…</font>

79
00:05:45,219 --> 00:05:46,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你手上是什么？</font>

80
00:05:47,119 --> 00:05:50,279
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">刚才告别的时候 风靡小姐给我的</font>

81
00:05:50,499 --> 00:05:53,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说是要戒烟 所以送给我了</font>

82
00:05:53,879 --> 00:05:59,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">原来如此 是把自己最重要的东西托付给久别重逢的男人</font>

83
00:06:00,339 --> 00:06:03,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那托付得可太多了 抽到一半的烟 打火机</font>

84
00:06:03,919 --> 00:06:05,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">甚至还有连环杀人案</font>

85
00:06:07,229 --> 00:06:09,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以敌人的目的是什么？</font>

86
00:06:10,119 --> 00:06:13,169
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么刻耳柏洛斯会到处夺取人的心脏？</font>

87
00:06:14,089 --> 00:06:17,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">很难想象人会在个人的判断下一直做这种事情</font>

88
00:06:18,879 --> 00:06:21,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我觉得这肯定是在上头的指示下犯的罪行</font>

89
00:06:22,949 --> 00:06:25,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">上头？SPES吗？</font>

90
00:06:25,699 --> 00:06:29,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">反正只要抓住敌人让他坦白 就能明白敌人的目的了</font>

91
00:06:29,619 --> 00:06:31,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那你想到办法了吗？</font>

92
00:06:32,629 --> 00:06:37,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实我以前已经查过刻耳柏洛斯犯下的罪行了</font>

93
00:06:37,499 --> 00:06:41,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">毕竟你也不可能轻易放过这么大的案子</font>

94
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:48,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">敌人的鼻子很灵 不管我再怎么想要接近 都会马上逃走</font>

95
00:06:49,249 --> 00:06:55,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">蝙蝠是耳朵 那刻耳柏洛斯就是改造了鼻子的人造人吗</font>

96
00:06:57,749 --> 00:07:02,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但不知为何 尽管我们还在这个城市</font>

97
00:07:02,919 --> 00:07:04,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">刻耳柏洛斯却依然毫无顾忌地犯下罪行</font>

98
00:07:05,279 --> 00:07:06,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">陷阱吗？</font>

99
00:07:08,279 --> 00:07:10,689
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">其实我本来想说这是个机会的</font>

100
00:07:11,169 --> 00:07:14,589
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">确实也能说是个机会 但具体要怎么追捕对方？</font>

101
00:07:15,249 --> 00:07:19,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">反了 不是我们去追捕刻耳柏洛斯</font>

102
00:07:19,589 --> 00:07:22,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而是刻耳柏洛斯自己来追捕我们</font>

103
00:07:25,459 --> 00:07:28,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">难道你想拿我当诱饵？</font>

104
00:07:29,499 --> 00:07:31,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你也会做像样的推理了嘛</font>

105
00:07:32,949 --> 00:07:36,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好了 去一边喝下午茶一边开会</font>

106
00:07:36,969 --> 00:07:42,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这个世界只有你能出了杀人现场就去喝下午茶</font>

107
00:07:43,309 --> 00:07:47,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而且来这里之前 你不是刚吃了一顿周日烤肉？</font>

108
00:07:47,759 --> 00:07:50,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我平时就在高强度使用大脑</font>

109
00:07:50,629 --> 00:07:53,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以在三大欲望上都会强烈一些</font>

110
00:07:54,029 --> 00:07:56,159
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以才整天睡午觉吗？</font>

111
00:07:56,479 --> 00:07:59,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">早上起不来的你没资格说我</font>

112
00:08:00,619 --> 00:08:03,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">三大欲望都比普通人强…</font>

113
00:08:07,599 --> 00:08:10,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说错了 只是食欲和睡眠欲</font>

114
00:08:11,259 --> 00:08:13,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(酒店)</font>

115
00:08:13,339 --> 00:08:17,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">从和你周游世界开始 已经快3年了
(酒店)</font>

