<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(酒店)</font>

117
00:08:18,189 --> 00:08:20,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">感觉过得好快啊</font>

118
00:08:20,479 --> 00:08:23,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不要突然怀念过去</font>

119
00:08:23,809 --> 00:08:26,889
