00:13:00,949 --> 00:13:03,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">来得太慢了</font>

163
00:13:03,769 --> 00:13:05,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">能赶上不就好了</font>

164
00:13:06,559 --> 00:13:07,659
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">觉得孤单啦？</font>

165
00:13:09,939 --> 00:13:15,649
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">按照我这「鼻子」的观察 并没有发现你</font>

166
00:13:15,749 --> 00:13:16,899
