167
00:13:19,319 --> 00:13:23,539
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你没发现 这个房间从刚才开始就充满了特殊气体吗？</font>

168
00:13:23,779 --> 00:13:24,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">特殊气体？</font>

169
00:13:26,969 --> 00:13:32,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">难道说 你一开始就猜到会这样 往水里加了特殊气体？</font>

170
00:13:32,949 --> 00:13:35,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因此刻耳柏洛斯的嗅觉才会麻痹</font>

171
00:13:36,829 --> 00:13:39,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你还是这么周到啊</font>

172
00:13:40,179 --> 00:13:43,299
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为我相信你是一定会坚持住的</font>

173
00:13:44,019 --> 00:13:46,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以 我赢了</font>

174
00:13:47,119 --> 00:13:48,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">放弃吧</font>

175
00:13:49,769 --> 00:13:53,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我还不能被人抓住！</font>

176
00:13:56,599 --> 00:13:57,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没用的</font>

177
00:14:03,029 --> 00:14:04,029
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手！</font>

178
00:14:04,229 --> 00:14:05,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">休想逃！</font>

179
00:14:08,279 --> 00:14:09,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不讲道理啊！</font>

180
00:14:10,929 --> 00:14:12,829
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我还有着使命</font>

181
00:14:13,419 --> 00:14:18,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还需要一个 必须再得到一个活生生的心脏</font>

182
00:14:19,669 --> 00:14:21,789
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那就把你这个留下来吧</font>

183
00:14:32,529 --> 00:14:33,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手！</font>

184
00:14:35,099 --> 00:14:36,099
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">小心</font>

185
00:14:37,689 --> 00:14:43,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这还是我们第一次真正面对面吧 大侦探</font>

186
00:14:46,479 --> 00:14:47,489
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你是…</font>

187
00:14:49,179 --> 00:14:50,869
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我叫「赫尔」
