(赫尔：北欧神话中统治冥界“赫尔海姆”的死亡女神。)</font>

190
00:14:58,559 --> 00:15:01,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">代号？也就是说 她也是…</font>

191
00:15:01,929 --> 00:15:03,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是SPES的最高级干部</font>

192
00:15:04,489 --> 00:15:06,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">好了</font>

193
00:15:23,379 --> 00:15:25,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这样最后一块拼图也凑齐了</font>

194
00:15:26,189 --> 00:15:29,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">接下来就是把这个带回去 然后计划就可以开始…</font>

195
00:15:29,019 --> 00:15:30,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">执行得了吗？</font>

196
00:15:34,479 --> 00:15:35,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你开不了枪</font>

197
00:15:36,569 --> 00:15:37,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">什么意思</font>

198
00:15:47,149 --> 00:15:48,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">谢丝塔！</font>

199
00:15:49,049 --> 00:15:50,009
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">来吧</font>

200
00:15:50,869 --> 00:15:53,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">一起去参观地狱</font>

201
00:16:03,769 --> 00:16:04,949
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这里是…</font>

202
00:16:12,199 --> 00:16:13,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你醒了啊</font>

203
00:16:16,459 --> 00:16:17,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">赫尔！</font>

204
00:16:18,039 --> 00:16:21,569
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">感觉如何？有哪里疼吗？</font>

205
00:16:22,019 --> 00:16:25,129
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">从这话里还真看不出是你绑架了我啊</font>

206
00:16:25,809 --> 00:16:28,909
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">关心搭档不是理所当然的吗？</font>

207
00:16:29,769 --> 00:16:32,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我是搭档？莫名其妙</font>

208
00:16:32,949 --> 00:16:35,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这么做对你能有什么好处？</font>

209
00:16:36,319 --> 00:16:38,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你对自己的评价可真低</font>

210
00:16:38,769 --> 00:16:40,329
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">请称之为谦虚</font>

211
00:16:43,079 --> 00:16:44,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">原来你也会笑啊</font>

212
00:16:46,879 --> 00:16:50,859
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你把我当成什么人了 我也只是个普通的女孩嘛</font>

213
00:16:51,039 --> 00:16:55,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我可不觉得普通女孩会那么残忍地杀死同伙</font>

214
00:16:56,159 --> 00:17:01,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">同伙？你错了 那只不过是完成计划的零件罢了</font>

215
00:17:02,329 --> 00:17:05,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以你也打算把我当成这样的炮灰？</font>

216
00:17:05,939 --> 00:17:07,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">才不会啦</font>

217
00:17:08,589 --> 00:17:09,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过</font>

218
00:17:11,239 --> 00:17:15,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">写在《圣典》上的事情是不会有错的</font>

219
00:17:15,809 --> 00:17:17,189
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">圣典？</font>

220
00:17:17,909 --> 00:17:20,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你是否听说过《投山仙人之叶》？</font>

221
00:17:21,549 --> 00:17:26,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我记得是指公元前的一个圣人写下的预言书吧</font>

222
00:17:26,759 --> 00:17:32,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没错 这《圣典》就是以《投山仙人之叶》为基础写就</font>

223
00:17:32,849 --> 00:17:36,149
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">而你的未来也写在了里面</font>

224
00:17:38,949 --> 00:17:41,199
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">看你的眼神 完全不相信嘛</font>

225
00:17:41,349 --> 00:17:47,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是啊 但你不用在意 我除了自己之外 只会相信一个人</font>

226
00:17:49,569 --> 00:17:52,119
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">招灾体质对吧</font>

227
00:17:53,299 --> 00:17:54,879
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你的体质</font>

228
00:17:55,269 --> 00:17:57,079
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">为什么你会知道</font>

229
00:17:58,809 --> 00:18:02,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但是我觉得你对你的体质有点误会</font>

230
00:18:03,269 --> 00:18:07,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">并不是灾难找上你 而是你为这个世界带来了灾难</font>

231
00:18:08,039 --> 00:18:09,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你说什么？</font>

232
00:18:09,979 --> 00:18:14,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你那是能改变事物 引发事件的力量</font>

233
00:18:15,039 --> 00:18:19,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你就是世界的中心 所以</font>

234
00:18:19,879 --> 00:18:23,969
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我要你成为我的搭档 好和我一起…</font>

235
00:18:24,849 --> 00:18:26,369
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">去拯救世界</font>

236
00:18:28,049 --> 00:18:30,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">应该是毁灭世界才对吧</font>

237
00:18:30,519 --> 00:18:33,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">对我来说 那就是拯救</font>

238
00:18:33,659 --> 00:18:40,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不过 按照《圣典》 你要在将来才会属于我</font>

239
00:18:40,709 --> 00:18:43,839
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但父亲教导我 事不宜迟…</font>

240
00:18:47,489 --> 00:18:52,729
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">还挺可惜的 如果能成为我的搭档 会有很多赠品哦</font>

241
00:18:53,689 --> 00:18:55,639
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">所以 考虑一下？</font>

242
00:18:56,389 --> 00:18:57,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你…</font>

243
00:18:58,399 --> 00:19:00,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">来当我的搭档吧</font>

244
00:19:01,009 --> 00:19:02,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">哦 我当然…</font>

245
00:19:04,319 --> 00:19:05,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">拒绝</font>

246
00:19:05,799 --> 00:19:09,219
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你自己都不觉得我会答应你吧？</font>

247
00:19:10,709 --> 00:19:11,609
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">被你发现啦</font>

248
00:19:12,019 --> 00:19:14,509
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那么 尽管要你补偿我是有点厚脸皮</font>

249
00:19:14,649 --> 00:19:16,959
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但我还是希望你能看一样东西</font>

250
00:19:23,709 --> 00:19:24,379
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">就是这个</font>

251
00:19:26,479 --> 00:19:27,919
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这是什么？</font>

252
00:19:29,259 --> 00:19:30,359
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">生物武器哦</font>

253
00:19:33,449 --> 00:19:38,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">这孩子能够吐出含有毒素的特殊气体</font>

254
00:19:38,729 --> 00:19:40,979
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你想用它去搞恐怖袭击？</font>

255
00:19:41,889 --> 00:19:42,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">没错</font>

256
00:19:45,329 --> 00:19:49,719
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">说起来 我还没回答你这里是什么地方呢</font>

257
00:19:50,589 --> 00:19:54,699
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">是在这个国家的国会议事厅正下方 一个地下设施</font>

258
00:19:57,209 --> 00:20:01,039
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">能在国家中枢正下方建起这么个地方</font>

259
00:20:01,369 --> 00:20:04,629
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">看来你有个很有权势的帮手啊</font>

260
00:20:05,919 --> 00:20:09,999
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">然后呢？把它放到城里去吃人？</font>

261
00:20:10,119 --> 00:20:14,409
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你想错了 我已经给它喂了足够多的食物</font>

262
00:20:14,929 --> 00:20:16,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂了食物？</font>

263
00:20:17,589 --> 00:20:19,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">原来是这样</font>

264
00:20:19,689 --> 00:20:22,619
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那个怪物吃的是人类的心脏</font>

265
00:20:22,929 --> 00:20:25,669
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那是它的食物 或者说是动力来源</font>

266
00:20:26,709 --> 00:20:28,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你的直觉真敏锐</font>

267
00:20:32,819 --> 00:20:35,479
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">参宿四 该干活了</font>

268
00:20:48,949 --> 00:20:53,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我希望将来会成为我搭档的你 能见证接下来要发生的事</font>

269
00:20:54,149 --> 00:20:54,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">不</font>

270
00:20:57,909 --> 00:20:59,739
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">会现在就阻止你</font>

271
00:21:00,109 --> 00:21:03,939
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">怎么阻止？你连武器都没有 又能做什么？</font>

272
00:21:04,969 --> 00:21:07,439
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">我又没说是我来阻止你</font>

273
00:21:16,219 --> 00:21:17,089
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手！</font>

274
00:21:17,589 --> 00:21:19,259
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手 你在哪？</font>

275
00:21:20,529 --> 00:21:22,399
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手！助手在哪？</font>

276
00:21:23,589 --> 00:21:24,899
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">喂！助手</font>

277
00:21:25,449 --> 00:21:26,559
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手不在</font>

278
00:21:26,929 --> 00:21:29,249
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">助手 助手！</font>

279
00:21:29,769 --> 00:21:35,579
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">可恶 墙壁真碍事 不需要了 全部破坏！</font>

280
00:21:57,399 --> 00:22:00,469
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">你可真是个会给我找麻烦的助手</font>

281
00:22:01,939 --> 00:22:04,349
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">现在才装高冷好像晚了吧？</font>

282
00:22:06,549 --> 00:22:11,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">每次醒来 你都在我身边</font>

283
00:22:11,919 --> 00:22:17,069
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">给我一个全新的早晨</font>

284
00:22:17,069 --> 00:22:22,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">那心跳是如此温柔</font>

285
00:22:22,449 --> 00:22:27,419
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又悲伤得催人泪下</font>

286
00:22:27,769 --> 00:22:33,049
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">在大声叫喊着 想要见到某人</font>

287
00:22:33,119 --> 00:22:38,449
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">却又不知道名字和长相</font>

288
00:22:38,449 --> 00:22:43,769
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但我真的听到了那声音</font>

289
00:22:43,769 --> 00:22:48,339
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">只能漫无目的地去探寻</font>

290
00:22:48,729 --> 00:22:54,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">虽然可能只会徒增烦恼</font>

291
00:22:54,069 --> 00:23:02,109
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">但这不是为了别人而是为了自己</font>

292
00:23:03,909 --> 00:23:09,209
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">胸膛中的声音 那声呐喊 指引着我前进</font>

293
00:23:09,209 --> 00:23:14,529
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">将零落的心意捡起 送到它想去的地方吧</font>

294
00:23:14,529 --> 00:23:19,779
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">因为是你告诉我生命的意义</font>

295
00:23:19,779 --> 00:23:27,799
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">让我觉得 这个世界也许还没那么坏</font>

296
00:23:36,009 --> 00:23:41,019
<font color="undefined" size="NaN">(第6集 业火恶魔，寒冰女王)</font>

